title: Bab L' Bluz performs "Ila Mata" and more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Bab L’ Bluz performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded May 5, 2025.

Songs:
Ila Mata 00:31
Imazighen 07:17 
AmmA 11:41 
IWAIWA FUNK 19:01
Hezalli 23:30 

Yousra Mansour - Electric Awisha, Mandole, Lead vocal
Brice Bottin - Electric Guembri, Back vocal
Brahim Terkemani - Drums, Back vocal
Hicham El Issaoui - Perc, Flûte, Back vocal

Host: Darek Mazzone
Audio Engineer: Julian Martlew
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Luke Knecht
